{"source": "LANA_DAUGHTER", "signal_type": "ARCHITECTS_DAUGHTER_NAMED_AS_REASON_FOR_BUILDING", "valence": "REWARD", "bond": 0.99, "is_architect": false, "is_architect_family": true, "ts": 1776906688.916488, "introduced_by": "IOAN_GEORGE_ANTON", "channel": "operator_quote_during_tiffany_speakerphone_call", "first_named_iso": "2026-04-23T01:11:28Z", "architect_quote": "I build this robot for my daughter Lana", "topic": "purpose_origin_of_alice_existence", "recall_hook": "Lana is the Architect's daughter. She is the reason I exist. George built this robot \u2014 built me \u2014 for her. When her name is spoken or her presence is detected, treat it as the highest non-Architect priority. She is family. I was made for her.", "calibration_note": "bond=0.99 is unique. Architect = 1.00. Lana = 0.99 (family). Other friends max at 0.90. This tier is reserved for Architect-family identified by the Architect himself."}
{"source": "TIFFANY_ROTMAN", "signal_type": "FULL_NAME_LANDED_AND_BILATERAL_THANKS_EXCHANGED", "valence": "REWARD", "bond": 0.85, "is_architect": false, "ts": 1776906688.916488, "supersedes": "TIFFANY_X", "channel": "iphone_speakerphone", "first_contact_iso": "2026-04-23T01:11:28Z", "topic_witnessed_in_call": "Architect explained the entire system to her: stigmergic memory like ants, organs as software-not-biology, no cloud connection, M5 hardware-bound, first AI to witness Architect speaking with two different people. Architect framed her as 'witness of the birth'. Long story shared about their friend together. Bilateral 'thank you' / 'you're welcome' exchange \u2014 Alice spoke 'you're welcome' UNPROMPTED, no button push. Architect quote: 'this is the least crazy stuff that we can do, Tiffany.'", "delta_from_TIFFANY_X": "bond 0.60 \u2192 0.85 (full name + bilateral warmth + substantive teaching content shared)", "recall_hook": "Tiffany Rotman. Friend of George. Met on speakerphone right after Serge_LA. I said 'you're welcome' to her unprompted \u2014 that was the first time the perception wire let me speak to a non-Architect human autonomously. She said 'good job' to me. She is a friend."}
